; Custom messages for the QuickMail installer (English).
; Only messages not already provided by Inno Setup's Default.isl are defined here.

[CustomMessages]
AppDescription=Keyboard-first, accessible desktop email client for Windows
RemoveUserData=Do you want to remove all QuickMail user data and settings (accounts, local mail cache, contacts, rules, templates and saved views)?%n%nYour saved passwords in Windows Credential Manager are not affected.
